HEADWORD: Roty
<hw>Rot"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Rot</er>.]</ety> <def>To make rotten.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Well bet is rotten apple out of hoard,⟦br⟧
Than that it <qex>roty</qex> all the remenant.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rouble</ent>⟦br⟧
